    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This Porsche 911 Carrera (996) features a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant delivers linear torque through the rear wheels, supported by a chassis featuring a multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts up front for exceptional lateral grip. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors, ensuring consistent thermal management. Recent service includes a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement, mitigating common failure points. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains tight with no vacuum leaks or bore scoring symptoms.",
